{"thi-ap25:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap25:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap25:0.3":"5 Nandatheriapadana ","thi-ap25:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap25:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap25:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap25:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap25:2.1":"Ovadako vinnapako, ","thi-ap25:2.2":"tarako sabbapaninam; ","thi-ap25:2.3":"Desanakusalo buddho, ","thi-ap25:2.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","thi-ap25:3.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","thi-ap25:3.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","thi-ap25:3.3":"Sampatte titthiye sabbe, ","thi-ap25:3.4":"pancasile patitthapi. ","thi-ap25:4.1":"Evam nirakulam asi, ","thi-ap25:4.2":"sunnatam titthiyehi ca; ","thi-ap25:4.3":"Vicittam arahantehi, ","thi-ap25:4.4":"vasibhutehi tadibhi. ","thi-ap25:5.1":"Ratananatthapannasam, ","thi-ap25:5.2":"uggatova mahamuni; ","thi-ap25:5.3":"Kancanagghiyasankaso, ","thi-ap25:5.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","thi-ap25:6.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","thi-ap25:6.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","thi-ap25:6.3":"Tavata titthamano so, ","thi-ap25:6.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","thi-ap25:7.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap25:7.2":"jata setthikule ahum; ","thi-ap25:7.3":"Nanaratanapajjote, ","thi-ap25:7.4":"mahasukhasamappita. ","thi-ap25:8.1":"Upetva tam mahaviram, ","thi-ap25:8.2":"assosim dhammadesanam; ","thi-ap25:8.3":"Amatam paramassadam, ","thi-ap25:8.4":"paramatthanivedakam. ","thi-ap25:9.1":"Tada nimantayitvana, ","thi-ap25:9.2":"sasangham lokanayakam; ","thi-ap25:9.3":"Datva tassa mahadanam, ","thi-ap25:9.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi. ","thi-ap25:10.1":"Jhayininam bhikkhuninam, ","thi-ap25:10.2":"aggatthanamapatthayim; ","thi-ap25:10.3":"Nipacca sirasa dhiram, ","thi-ap25:10.4":"sasangham lokanayakam. ","thi-ap25:11.1":"Tada adantadamako, ","thi-ap25:11.2":"tilokasarano pabhu; ","thi-ap25:11.3":"Byakasi narasarathi, ","thi-ap25:11.4":"‘lacchase tam supatthitam. ","thi-ap25:12.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap25:12.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap25:12.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap25:12.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap25:13.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap25:13.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap25:13.3":"Nandati nama namena, ","thi-ap25:13.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap25:14.1":"Tam sutva mudita hutva, ","thi-ap25:14.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","thi-ap25:14.3":"Mettacitta paricarim, ","thi-ap25:14.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","thi-ap25:15.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap25:15.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap25:15.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap25:15.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap25:16.1":"Tato cuta yamamagam, ","thi-ap25:16.2":"tatoham tusitam gata; ","thi-ap25:16.3":"Tato ca nimmanaratim, ","thi-ap25:16.4":"vasavattipuram tato. ","thi-ap25:17.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap25:17.2":"tassa kammassa vahasa; ","thi-ap25:17.3":"Tattha tattheva rajunam, ","thi-ap25:17.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap25:18.1":"Tato cuta manussatte, ","thi-ap25:18.2":"rajanam cakkavattinam; ","thi-ap25:18.3":"Mandalinanca rajunam, ","thi-ap25:18.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap25:19.1":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","thi-ap25:19.2":"devesu manujesu ca; ","thi-ap25:19.3":"Sabbattha sukhita hutva, ","thi-ap25:19.4":"nekakappesu samsarim. ","thi-ap25:20.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","thi-ap25:20.2":"suramme kapilavhaye; ","thi-ap25:20.3":"Ranno suddhodanassaham, ","thi-ap25:20.4":"dhita asim anindita. ","thi-ap25:21.1":"Siriya rupinim disva, ","thi-ap25:21.2":"nanditam asi tam kulam; ","thi-ap25:21.3":"Tena nandati me namam, ","thi-ap25:21.4":"sundaram pavaram ahu. ","thi-ap25:22.1":"Yuvatinanca sabbasam, ","thi-ap25:22.2":"kalyaniti ca vissuta; ","thi-ap25:22.3":"Tasmimpi nagare ramme, ","thi-ap25:22.4":"thapetva tam yasodharam. ","thi-ap25:23.1":"Jettho bhata tilokaggo, ","thi-ap25:23.2":"pacchimo araha tatha; ","thi-ap25:23.3":"Ekakini gahatthaham, ","thi-ap25:23.4":"matara paricodita. ","thi-ap25:24.1":"‘Sakiyamhi kule jata, ","thi-ap25:24.2":"putte buddhanuja tuvam; ","thi-ap25:24.3":"Nandenapi vina bhuta, ","thi-ap25:24.4":"agare kim nu acchasi. ","thi-ap25:25.1":"Jaravasanam yobbannam, ","thi-ap25:25.2":"rupam asucisammatam; ","thi-ap25:25.3":"Rogantamapicarogyam, ","thi-ap25:25.4":"jivitam maranantikam. ","thi-ap25:26.1":"Idampi te subham rupam, ","thi-ap25:26.2":"sasikantam manoharam; ","thi-ap25:26.3":"Bhusananam alankaram, ","thi-ap25:26.4":"sirisanghatasannibham. ","thi-ap25:27.1":"Punjitam lokasaramva, ","thi-ap25:27.2":"nayananam rasayanam; ","thi-ap25:27.3":"Punnanam kittijananam, ","thi-ap25:27.4":"ukkakakulanandanam. ","thi-ap25:28.1":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap25:28.2":"jara samadhisessati; ","thi-ap25:28.3":"Vihaya geham karunne, ","thi-ap25:28.4":"cara dhammamanindite’. ","thi-ap25:29.1":"Sutvaham matu vacanam, ","thi-ap25:29.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thi-ap25:29.3":"Dehena na tu cittena, ","thi-ap25:29.4":"rupayobbanalalita. ","thi-ap25:30.1":"Mahata ca payattena, ","thi-ap25:30.2":"jhanajjhena param mama; ","thi-ap25:30.3":"Katunca vadate mata, ","thi-ap25:30.4":"na caham tattha ussuka. ","thi-ap25:31.1":"Tato mahakaruniko, ","thi-ap25:31.2":"disva mam kamalalasam; ","thi-ap25:31.3":"Nibbindanattham rupasmim, ","thi-ap25:31.4":"mama cakkhupathe jino. ","thi-ap25:32.1":"Sakena anubhavena, ","thi-ap25:32.2":"itthim mapesi sobhinim; ","thi-ap25:32.3":"Dassaniyam suruciram, ","thi-ap25:32.4":"mamatopi surupinim. ","thi-ap25:33.1":"Tamaham vimhita disva, ","thi-ap25:33.2":"ativimhitadehinim; ","thi-ap25:33.3":"Cintayim ‘saphalam meti, ","thi-ap25:33.4":"nettalabhanca manusam. ","thi-ap25:34.1":"Tamaham ehi subhage, ","thi-ap25:34.2":"yenattho tam vadehi me; ","thi-ap25:34.3":"Kulam te namagottanca, ","thi-ap25:34.4":"vada me yadi te piyam. ","thi-ap25:35.1":"Na vancakalo subhage, ","thi-ap25:35.2":"ucchange mam nivasaya; ","thi-ap25:35.3":"Sidantiva mamangani, ","thi-ap25:35.4":"pasuppaya muhuttakam’. ","thi-ap25:36.1":"Tato sisam mamange sa, ","thi-ap25:36.2":"katva sayi sulocana; ","thi-ap25:36.3":"Tassa nalate patita, ","thi-ap25:36.4":"luddha paramadaruna. ","thi-ap25:37.1":"Saha tassa nipatena, ","thi-ap25:37.2":"pilaka upapajjatha; ","thi-ap25:37.3":"Paggharimsu pabhinna ca, ","thi-ap25:37.4":"kunapa pubbalohita. ","thi-ap25:38.1":"Pabhinnam vadanancapi, ","thi-ap25:38.2":"kunapam putigandhanam; ","thi-ap25:38.3":"Uddhumatam vinilanca, ","thi-ap25:38.4":"pubbancapi sarirakam. ","thi-ap25:39.1":"Sa paveditasabbangi, ","thi-ap25:39.2":"nissasanti muhum muhum; ","thi-ap25:39.3":"Vedayanti sakam dukkham, ","thi-ap25:39.4":"karunam paridevayi. ","thi-ap25:40.1":"‘Dukkhena dukkhita homi, ","thi-ap25:40.2":"phusayanti ca vedana; ","thi-ap25:40.3":"Mahadukkhe nimuggamhi, ","thi-ap25:40.4":"saranam hohi me sakhi. ","thi-ap25:41.1":"Kuhim vadanasobham te, ","thi-ap25:41.2":"kuhim te tunganasika; ","thi-ap25:41.3":"Tambabimbavarottham te, ","thi-ap25:41.4":"vadanam te kuhim gatam. ","thi-ap25:42.1":"Kuhim sasinibham vannam, ","thi-ap25:42.2":"kambugiva kuhim gata; ","thi-ap25:42.3":"Dolalolava te kanna, ","thi-ap25:42.4":"vevannam samupagata. ","thi-ap25:43.1":"Makulakharakakara, ","thi-ap25:43.2":"kalikava payodhara; ","thi-ap25:43.3":"Pabhinna putikunapa, ","thi-ap25:43.4":"dutthagandhittamagata. ","thi-ap25:44.1":"Vedimajjhava sussoni, ","thi-ap25:44.2":"sunava nitakibbisa; ","thi-ap25:44.3":"Jata amejjhabharita, ","thi-ap25:44.4":"aho rupamasassatam. ","thi-ap25:45.1":"Sabbam sarirasanjatam, ","thi-ap25:45.2":"putigandham bhayanakam; ","thi-ap25:45.3":"Susanamiva bibhaccham, ","thi-ap25:45.4":"ramante yattha balisa’. ","thi-ap25:46.1":"Tada mahakaruniko, ","thi-ap25:46.2":"bhata me lokanayako; ","thi-ap25:46.3":"Disva samviggacittam mam, ","thi-ap25:46.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","thi-ap25:47.1":"‘Aturam kunapam putim, ","thi-ap25:47.2":"passa nande samussayam; ","thi-ap25:47.3":"Asubhaya cittam bhavehi, ","thi-ap25:47.4":"ekaggam susamahitam. ","thi-ap25:48.1":"Yatha idam tatha etam, ","thi-ap25:48.2":"yatha etam tatha idam; ","thi-ap25:48.3":"Duggandham putikam vati, ","thi-ap25:48.4":"balanam abhinanditam. ","thi-ap25:49.1":"Evametam avekkhanti, ","thi-ap25:49.2":"rattindivamatandita; ","thi-ap25:49.3":"Tato sakaya pannaya, ","thi-ap25:49.4":"abhinibbijjha dakkhasi’. ","thi-ap25:50.1":"Tatoham atisamvigga, ","thi-ap25:50.2":"sutva gatha subhasita; ","thi-ap25:50.3":"Tatratthitavaham santi, ","thi-ap25:50.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap25:51.1":"Yattha yattha nisinnaham, ","thi-ap25:51.2":"sada jhanaparayana; ","thi-ap25:51.3":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","thi-ap25:51.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","thi-ap25:52.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap25:52.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap25:52.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap25:53.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap25:53.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap25:53.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap25:54.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap25:54.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap25:54.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap25:55.1":"Ittham sudam nanda bhikkhuni janapadakalyani ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap25:56.1":"Nandatheriyapadanam pancamam. "}